---
title: Spiced Chicken and Pepper Stew with garlic rice and creme fraiche
description: Subtle Central American-inspired spices are a big part of this comforting and warming dish. Chicken and peppers in a tomato-based stew top fragrant garlic rice, while a dollop of creme fraiche provides a cooling element to a simple and satisfying meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W14_IE_IEXCFC21686-3_Main_high-e397edb8.jpg
